{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<mover>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p class=\"summary\">MathML の <code>&lt;mover&gt;</code> 要素はアクセントかリミットを上に載せるために使われます。構文は次の通りです： <code>&lt;mover&gt; <em>base overscript</em> &lt;/mover&gt;</code><br>\n 訳注：アクセントは例えばドットやハットなどの記号です。リミットとは，定積分の区間の端点などのことです。<br>\n overscript には定着した訳語がないようです。superscript（上付き）が肩に付く添字であるのに対し，overscript は真上に付く添字です。そのまま「オーバースクリプト」と書くことにします。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"attr-accent\">accent</dt>\n <dd>これが <code>true</code> の場合，オーバースクリプトはアクセントであり，本体に近く表示されます。<br>\n <code>false</code>（既定値）の場合，オーバースクリプトは本体の上に載せるリミットです。<br>\n 訳注：既定値は実際にはもう少し複雑で，オーバースクリプトが <code>&lt;mo&gt;</code> 要素の場合，その <code>accent</code> 属性が既定値となるというルールがあります。詳細は仕様書を参照。また，<code>accent</code> 属性の値によって大きさが違って表示される場合もあります。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-align\">align</dt>\n <dd>オーバースクリプトの揃え位置。取り得る値は：<code>left</code>, <code>center</code> および <code>right</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-class-id-style\">class, id, style</dt>\n <dd>Provided for use with <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS\">stylesheets</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-href\">href</dt>\n <dd>Used to set a hyperlink to a specified URI.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>The background color. You can use <code>#rgb</code>, <code>#rrggbb</code> and <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">HTML color names</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathcolor\">mathcolor</dt>\n <dd>The text color. You can use <code>#rgb</code>, <code>#rrggbb</code> and <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">HTML color names</a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Sample rendering: <img alt=\"x+y+z\" src=\"/files/3196/mover.png\" style=\"margin-left: 10px; vertical-align: middle;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>Rendering in your browser: <math> <mover accent=\"true\"> <mrow> <mi> x </mi> <mo> + </mo> <mi> y </mi> <mo> + </mo> <mi> z </mi> </mrow> <mo> ⏞ </mo> </mover> </math></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mover</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">accent</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> x <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> + <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> y <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> + <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> z <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token entity\" title=\"⏞\">&amp;#x23DE;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--TOP CURLY BRACKET--&gt;</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mover</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様書","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.mover\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">mover の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.mover\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">mover の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"ブラウザ実装状況","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.mover","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\" title=\"<munder>\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></code> (Underscript)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munderover&gt; (en-US)</a></code> (Underscript-overscript pair)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"ブラウザ実装状況"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"MathML の <mover> 要素はアクセントかリミットを上に載せるために使われます。構文は次の通りです： <mover> base overscript </mover>\n 訳注：アクセントは例えばドットやハットなどの記号です。リミットとは，定積分の区間の端点などのことです。\n overscript には定着した訳語がないようです。superscript（上付き）が肩に付く添字であるのに対し，overscript は真上に付く添字です。そのまま「オーバースクリプト」と書くことにします。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<mover>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<mover>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<mover>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<mover>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mathml/element/mover","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/mathml/element/mover/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML 要素リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover","title":"<mover>"}],"pageTitle":"<mover> - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}